⦿ .spun — the five-fold spin of Seth Ryan
node AHX · AHX · ⟦Seth Ryan:AHX:f3a197⟧

WHO   — Seth Ryan — the foot-soldier
WHAT  — The movement at its ugliest and least glamorous: the bigotry stripped of Derek's articulacy, just rage and slurs.
WHERE — AHX · American History X (1998)  Framework inputs: American History X (1998, dir. Tony Kaye, New Line); verified cast & facts  Conductor / external anchor: ROOT0 (catalogued into UD0)
WHY   — Because the film shows hate at every register — and Seth is its dumbest, plainest face.
HOW   — By filling Derek's vacated role as Danny's influence, all venom and no charisma.

awareness — what the node knows of itself:
  Derek had the speeches. I've just got the hate, plain and loud — and the kid was listening to me while his brother was gone.

